items.title: Judge to decide fate of Trump's federal buyout offer
items.description: A federal judge in Boston Monday will consider whether to block President Trump's plan to buy out tens of thousands of federal employees.

items.title: WATCH:  Thieves begin targeting eggs
items.description: The bird flu outbreak has sent the price of eggs to record highs, leading to egg thefts in Seattle and Pennsylvania.
